org.modelio.vbasic.auth

Class AuthData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.vbasic.auth.AuthData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAuthData
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NoneAuthData, UnknownAuthData, UserPasswordAuthData

    public abstract class AuthData
extends Object
implements IAuthData
    Base class for Authentication data used to connect to remote locations.

    All authentication datas are stored in a Properties field. Sub classes are not intended to add others.
